          "description": "My experience at SmileSpace Dentistry in Harlem is always a pleasure! From the moment I walk in, the staff is warm, welcoming, and professional. The office is clean, modern, and creates a comfortable atmosphere that helps put patients at ease.\n\nThe dentists and hygienists take the time to explain everything clearly and genuinely care about their patients' oral health and comfort. I never feel rushed, and every visit is handled with kindness, patience, and attention to detail.\n\nIf you're looking for a dental office in Harlem that provides excellent care and outstanding customer service, I highly recommend SmileSpace Dentistry. They consistently make going to the dentist a positive experience!\n\n10/10 \u2014 I'll definitely continue coming back! \ud83d\ude01\ud83e\uddb7\u2728",
