          "description": "I\u2019ve never had a better experience. Let\u2019s start with the ambience the music made me feel calm. The staff was ever so welcoming. Usually dental visits make me feel the most anxiety. I\u2019m ashamed to say that I was afraid to go to the dentist, especially coming in from Florida. My experience today was hands-down, the greatest dental experience I\u2019ve ever had. I did not feel one drill Not an ounce of discomfort. It\u2019s not like I had great teeth to start with, but the amount of work that they did and the amount of comfort that I felt, no only will I be returning, I honestly will never go to another dentist ever again If it isn\u2019t small space.",
