          "description": "The quality and exceptional service did not begin when I arrived to SmileSpace for my dental care. It began when I called to make an appointment. The receptionist was courteous and helpful.\n\nThe hygienist was magnificent----caring, personable, super gentle yet thorough and knowledgeable. She made me feel so comfortable and relaxed. The entire office staff was quite proficient. I rate my experience as one of the best that I've ever had. Everyone in the office, from the moment that I walked in, to the moment that I was called to start the cleaning and examination, to the dentist providing her assessment and recommendations, I was 1,000% satisfied. I've already recommended SmileSpace to my family and will recommend to my friends as well.\n\nThank you, SmileSpace, for the experience of a lifetime. See you again soon!\n\nG. Spry",
