          "description": "I\u2019ve been coming to Smile Space for over six months, and today I brought my 11-year-old for his appointment with Dr. Black. It was, without a doubt, the best dentist experience we\u2019ve both ever had.\n\nDr. Black\u2019s bedside manner is exceptional. He took the time to explain everything in a way my son could understand, and he was warm, patient, and genuinely engaging. It\u2019s incredibly rare to find a dentist who truly cares and connects like this.\n\nI don\u2019t even have enough words to describe how positive this experience was for both of us. If you haven\u2019t met Dr. Black yet, book an appointment, you won\u2019t regret it. I truly can\u2019t recommend him enough!!!",
