          "description": "Smilespace is such an amazing facility . I started off in the Brooklyn office originally with my teeth whitening services which was always a 10 out of 10 experience. The amount of complements I would receive were insane . To the point people would assume that they were cosmetically done . I transitioned to the Harlem office because it\u2019s closer to my home and I\u2019m just more impressed every time . The facility is so beautiful && clean and aesthetically pleasing. Everyone is so warm and welcoming . I feel like I\u2019m apart of such an amazing dental community . I get a teeth cleaning every 4 months and started Invisalign and when I tell you I actually look forward to my appointments I truly mean it . I\u2019ve been doing my Invisalign for almost a year now and I\u2019m just about completed soon and when I tell you my smile and teeth structure is so aligned and beautiful. I was so skeptical about it initially because i never knew anyone who had done Invisalign and i was unsure about how successful I would be with it but everyone over at smile space educated me so thoroughly. From answering my concerns to educating me on the proper care through out my process . I\u2019m just so happy to share my experience and let anyone who\u2019s thinking about coming to smile space to definitely do ! You will not regret it , you\u2019ll be thanking me later while writing there next review .",
